headline: Oscar Mayer Hotdogger Applications are Officially Open: Now is your Chance to Get Behind the Wheel of an American Icon
summary: CHICAGO & PITTSBURGH, December 18, 2024--Today, Oscar Mayer announced the opening of Hotdogger applications, inviting recent college graduates to apply for a one-year, full-time gig behind the wheel of the iconic Wienermobile. Open now through January 31, the relished position offers fans the opportunity to become official spokespeople of the brand while living out its mission of sparking smiles.
